        {
            "title": "茶飲股逆勢領升港股，滬上阿姨月升近 80%！中國新茶飲出海刷屏",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nxPpFXPmPXGhujCjzaDxTQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC4H0HF_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周三，4月22日，港股三大指數集體調整，恒科指跌超2%，茶飲股逆勢上升，滬上阿姨 (HK:2589)大升15%，月內累計升幅近80%，茶百道 (HK:2555)升超14%，奈雪的茶 (HK:2150)升超3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年4月，中國連鎖經營協會發佈了「2026中國餐飲/新茶飲出海品牌50榜單」。榜單顯示，蜜雪冰城海外門店數量超過4000家，霸王茶姬海外門店超過200家，喜茶、茶百道、奈雪的茶、茶話弄、茉莉奶白等品牌也開設了若干海外門店。許多消費者在這些海外門店前排隊數小時，只為一品「東方味道」，中國新茶飲已成為名副其實的「排隊王」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7cdcc464-0b82-3d2a-af75-bdf5672c1b9a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中信建投指出，茶飲龍頭仍維持穩定增速，預計26H1平台仍有補貼或龍頭精准補貼，龍頭有望憑藉補貼錯期和自身優質成長及補坪效措施帶來明年初優質同店驗證。華源證券則指出，現制茶飲方面，建議關注品牌力較強且業務覆蓋區域較廣的頭部茶飲品牌，如蜜雪集團、古茗。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>限時閃購：</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro </span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>55% </span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣！重磅財報預測資料，一站式查看，助你未雨綢繆，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"401\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZTWgQI9scTLebQ5Alr2mWQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQwMQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/772a36c27e19a5d73905cfad4b39d653\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
