        {
            "title": "財經｜現貨金反彈0.8%企穩4740美元  特朗普考慮延長停火",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜現貨金反彈0.8%企穩4740美元 特朗普考慮延長停火\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜現貨金反彈0.8%企穩4740美元 特朗普考慮延長停火</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現貨黃金早盤報每盎司4740美元附近，反彈0.8%至4756美元，昨日曾創逾兩周低位4668美元，單日最大跌幅近2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普於美股收市後表示正考慮延長美伊停火協議，緩解市場對霍爾木茲海峽封鎖同能源危機嘅擔憂，帶動避險資金回流黃金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4月17日停火談判僵局一度令金價急挫，但最新消息指伊朗同意兩周延長，市場情緒改善。COMEX黃金期貨同步升0.81%報4757美元，全球央行購金需求仍強。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8%E9%87%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%880-8-%E4%BC%81%E7%A9%A94740%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB-033039211.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 11:42:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中東戰事下人民幣資產熱度不退 財政部在港點心債創發行利率新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國財政部周三在香港發行2023年以來最大規模的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"人民幣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:人民幣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人民幣\">人民幣</a>主權債，部分品種發行利率創下彭博有紀錄來新低，顯示全球投資者對人民幣計價資產需求保持強勁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財政部公告顯示，在香港招標發行了4只人民幣主權債，規模共計155億元，涵蓋從2年期至15年期，認購倍數4.6倍，較2月份發行有所提高。彭博匯編數據顯示，其中2年期和15年期發行利率創下了紀錄新低，3年期和5年期品種均為2011年以來最低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港充足的人民幣流動性提供了有利的融資窗口，而中東戰事也利好人民幣資產吸引力。在此窗口下，財政部此次得以以低利率發行，藉機完善離岸人民幣殖利率曲線，並進一步推動人民幣國際化。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-12df36dd-398e-3e6b-bb38-4a8f2712fb5b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為衡量銀行間融資成本的重要指標，香港1個月期離岸人民幣Hibor周三報約1.50%，仍未遠離過去近一年來的低位。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
